        </param>
        <param>
          <type>const <ref refid="structSYN__Matrix" kindref="compound">SYN_Matrix</ref> *</type>
          <declname>z</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Update step: incorporate a measurement. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>After this call:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>x̂ is corrected toward the measurement</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>P is reduced (uncertainty decreased)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kf</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Kalman filter instance. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>z</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Measurement vector (n_meas × 1). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>SYN_OK on success, SYN_ERROR if innovation covariance is singular. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
